	   <a name=10366118353637></a>
	   <form action=http://www1.allakhazam.com/perl/strategy/mrate.pl name=f10366118353637><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=item.html?item=2111&mid=10366118353637>Crimson Robe of Alendine</a> <a id=fs8 href=item.html?item=2111&mid=10366118353637#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=182489><span id= >NorrathBakabaka</span></a>, <span id= > </span><br><span id=notbold>4 posts</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Wed, Nov 6th 3:04 PM 2002</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Good<span id=notbold>[3.50]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>I just received this robe in a very lop sided trade in my favor, for some quest items that I had. The robe is so special looking that you either love it or hate it. I absolutely love the look of it. Additionally, I feel that the stats are great. In almost every item that I see posts for, folks wish that it had more of this or more of that. Well, this robe does not have resists, however has great Int and good HP and Mana. Resists will need to come from other slots. Like anything else, it is a matter of what a person wants. With this robe on my Int is 228, raw mana 478, my resists are all over 100,I have five important focus items and my HP is quite good for my level. As I learn more about Norrath from more experienced adventures than me, it is not the stats of anyone item that is important, it is the total package that you put together for yourself. So are resists important yes, do you need them on a robe. No. not if you are carrying them elsewhere. Everyones' opinions are very valid. The bottom line is that I love the look of the robe, you seldom see it around, and it compliments my other slots statwise. I will never part from this robe and am very very happy to have it.<br>Safe journeys and good looting,<br>Bakabaka Khagan - Necromancer of Paineel<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
